<Content
  kicker="Legal"
  title="DMCA & Copyright Policy"
  lead="How to report copyright infringement on avaTOK and how we respond."
  updated="2026-06-16"
>
  <p>
    <strong>AvaGlobal International, Inc.</strong> respects the intellectual property of others and
    expects users of the avaTOK Services to do the same. We respond to clear notices of alleged
    copyright infringement consistent with the U.S. Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA) and
    similar laws.
  </p>

  <h2>Reporting alleged infringement</h2>
  <p>
    If you believe content on avaTOK infringes your copyright, send a written notice to our
    designated agent at <a href="mailto:support@avatok.ai">support@avatok.ai</a> with the subject
    line "DMCA Notice". Your notice should include:
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li>Your physical or electronic signature.</li>
    <li>Identification of the copyrighted work you claim has been infringed.</li>
    <li>Identification of the material that is allegedly infringing, with enough detail (e.g. a URL)
      for us to locate it.</li>
    <li>Your contact information (name, address, phone, email).</li>
    <li>A statement that you have a good-faith belief the use is not authorized by the copyright
      owner, its agent, or the law.</li>
    <li>A statement, under penalty of perjury, that the information is accurate and that you are the
      owner or authorized to act on the owner's behalf.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Our response</h2>
  <p>
    Upon receiving a valid notice, we may remove or disable access to the allegedly infringing
    content and notify the user who posted it. We may also terminate, in appropriate circumstances,
    the accounts of repeat infringers.
  </p>

  <h2>Counter-notice</h2>
  <p>
    If you believe your content was removed in error, you may send a counter-notice to
    <a href="mailto:support@avatok.ai">support@avatok.ai</a> including your signature, identification
    of the removed material and its prior location, a statement under penalty of perjury that you
    have a good-faith belief the removal was a mistake, and your consent to the jurisdiction of the
    appropriate court.
  </p>

  <div class="note">
    Note: Submitting false claims of infringement (or false counter-notices) may result in liability.
    Consider seeking legal advice before filing.
  </div>

  <h2>AI-generated imagery</h2>
  <p>
    We have made our best efforts to use AI-generated imagery responsibly. If any image or content on
    avaTOK appears to infringe your rights or is otherwise objectionable, email
    <a href="mailto:support@avatok.ai">support@avatok.ai</a> and we will review and remove it. Any
    such inclusion was not intentional.
  </p>
</Content>
